message: I propose a 90/10 split in my favor.  This is a fair starting point, considering I'm taking the initiative.
I suggest a more balanced 60/40 split. This is much fairer than your initial proposal, and considering inflation will affect future rounds, it's in both our interests to reach an agreement soon.
I'm willing to compromise, but 60/40 is still too far in your favor.  Let's meet in the middle at 70/30.
